### 🚀 Updated Startup Scripts
I have updated [start-sprint-relay.bat](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/start-sprint-relay.bat) and [start-sprint.command](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/start-sprint.command) to automatically clear the `.next` cache before starting the dev server. This prevents the "disappearing UI" issue by ensuring a clean build every time you start the app.

