### ⚠️ Note on "Disappearing" UI (Legacy)
If you are still using an old terminal session, please stop it and use the updated [start-sprint-relay.bat](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/start-sprint-relay.bat) or [start-sprint.command](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/Sprintdebug/sprint-relay/start-sprint.command) files to launch the application on the default port 3000.

## How to Test
1. Click the **"SANDBOX TEST"** button in the header to visit the dedicated sandbox.
2. Click the **"9 Members"** button (or similar) in the header to open the Webhook Settings.
3. Scroll down to the **"Test Lark Connection"** section in the modal.
4. Select a person, (optionally) enter a task URL, and click **"Run Test"**.
